query:
INSERT INTO
                snapshots (
                    VERSION,
                    l1_batch_number,
                    storage_logs_filepaths,
                    factory_deps_filepath,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
            VALUES
                (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    ARRAY_FILL('' :: TEXT, ARRAY [$3::INTEGER]),
                    $4,
                    NOW(),
                    NOW()
                )
